title: Create Access Token for Terraform in Proxmox
tags: @zettel _method proxmox terraform
roam-id: 046947de-3557-4341-a586-a1c558a16292
type: text/markdown

- watch this: <https://youtu.be/wK8PUp7rjzs>

- ssh into proxmox

  ``` shell
  pveum user add terraform@pam
  pveum user token add terraform@pam t2
  pveum acl modify / -user terraform@pam -role Administrator
  ```

- you want to disable privilege separation also
